---
name: text_sed
description: Stream-edit text with sed — substitute, delete, or print lines from stdin or a file, or rewrite a file in place. Use to apply a sed script in a pipeline or do a scripted find-and-replace across files.
kind: tool
tags: [text, sed, stream, substitute, replace]
use_when: [substitute text in a stream, find and replace in a file, sed in place edit, delete lines matching a pattern, print only matching lines, apply a sed script]
danger: medium
